file.name: swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  description: '<font size="2" color="red">MIT License</font>'
  title: "CHATBOT"
  contact:
    name: Erlan Lucio
    url: https://github.com/lucioerlan
  version: '1.0'
servers:
- url: http://localhost:5000
  variables: {}
paths:
  /get-view-chatbot:
    get:
      tags:
      - ROUTES
      summary: GET VIEW CHATBOT
      operationId: GETVIEWCHATBOT
      parameters: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          headers: {}
      deprecated: false
  /get-all-chatbot:
    get:
      tags:
      - ROUTES
      summary: GET ALL CHATBOT
      operationId: GETALLCHATBOT
      parameters:
      - name: input
        in: query
        description: ''
        required: true
        style: form
        explode: true
        schema:
          type: string
          example: ingredientes do slime?
      - name: activate
        in: query
        description: ''
        required: true
        style: form
        explode: true
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          example: 1
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          headers: {}
      deprecated: false
  /getid-chatbot:
    get:
      tags:
      - ROUTES
      summary: GET ID CHATBOT
      operationId: GETIDCHATBOT
      parameters:
      - name: id
        in: query
        description: ''
        required: true
        style: form
        explode: true
        schema:
          type: string
          example: 60cd7e92ec5cef2a444d21cc
      - name: Content-Type
        in: header
        description: ''
        required: true
        style: simple
        schema:
          type: string
          example: application/json
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          headers: {}
      deprecated: false
  /store-chatbot:
    post:
      tags:
      - ROUTES
      summary: STORE CHATBOT
      operationId: STORECHATBOT
      parameters: []
      requestBody:
        description: ''
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/STORECHATBOTREQUEST'
            example:
              activate: 1
              input: 'Atenas, Onde fica? '
              output: na Grécia
        required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          headers: {}
      deprecated: false
  /update-chatbot:
    put:
      tags:
      - ROUTES
      summary: UPDATE CHATBOT
      operationId: UPDATECHATBOT
      parameters: []
      requestBody:
        description: ''
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/UPDATECHATBOTREQUEST'
            example:
              id: 60cd90cc12acc32accb0e60b
              activate: 1
              input: 'Atenas, Onde fica? '
              output: na Grécia.
        required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          headers: {}
      deprecated: false
components:
  schemas:
    STORECHATBOTREQUEST:
      title: STORECHATBOTREQUEST
      required:
      - activate
      - input
      - output
      type: object
      properties:
        activate:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        input:
          type: string
        output:
          type: string
      example:
        activate: 1
        input: 'Atenas, Onde fica? '
        output: na Grécia
    UPDATECHATBOTREQUEST:
      title: UPDATECHATBOTREQUEST
      required:
      - id
      - activate
      - input
      - output
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        activate:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        input:
          type: string
        output:
          type: string
      example:
        id: 60cd90cc12acc32accb0e60b
        activate: 1
        input: 'Atenas, Onde fica? '
        output: na Grécia.
tags:
- name: ROUTES
